4. SETUP INSTRUCTIONS
prerequisites
1. Node.js [Download here](https://nodejs.org/)
   * Verify installation:
     ```bash
     node -v
     npm -v
     ```

2. **MongoDB** (local or cloud using [MongoDB Atlas](https://www.mongodb.com/atlas))
   * Verify installation (local):
     ```bash
     mongod --version
     ```
   * Start MongoDB service:
     ```bash
     mongod
     ```
3. **Code Editor** → [VS Code](https://code.visualstudio.com/)
4. **Postman or cURL** → for API testing



